casebody.data:
No. 9,

Orig.

United States v. Louisiana et al.

Report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Replies thereto, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 30 days.

Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this order.

[For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 464 U. S. 927.]
